descriptionHtml:
Description:
############
This is an Old Cellar, at the back of the Breezehhome. It is a small Player owned Trophyroom and Storagearea, there are also areas for all your needs. 

Features:
##############
- Playerhome in Whiterun
- Crafting Area 
- Cooking Pot
- BedÂ´s
- Indoor Storage (Chest, Display, Books, Weapon,Armor)
- Throne

Installing:
##############
- Extract .ESP to your Data folder and make sure it is checked in the DATA section of your Skyrim Launcher.

Removal:
#########
- MAKE SURE that everything is removed from the house, this entire zone will be GONE when you delete it, so make sure to remove everything first or it will be GONE.
